expected_answers.exploit_name: Factory deploy reverts instead of returning address when account already exists
expected_answers.description_summary: Factory.deploy uses create2 but reverts with CreateCollision if address exists, violating ERC-4337 expectation to return address. Breaks simulations and bundler logic.
